name: Dianna Whitley
what_you_do: Dianna Whitley is a certified hypnotherapist and coach who helps people break negative habits and establish positive ones through hypnosis delivered via Zoom or in-person sessions.
who_you_serve: Individuals and business people/entrepreneurs seeking to overcome personal challenges (weight loss, smoking, anxiety, sleep) or business obstacles (confidence, procrastination, limiting beliefs).
social_proof: 25 years of experience as a certified hypnotherapist; has helped over 7,000 people with personal challenges; author of 'Staying Young at Any Age'; Ambassador with AZ Women Networking.
signature_programs: Staying Young at Any Age (book); stress reduction audio (free); programs for weight loss, stop smoking, anxiety/stress reduction, confidence, sleep
business_focus: Helping individuals and entrepreneurs reprogram their subconscious mind through hypnosis to eliminate negative habits and achieve personal and professional goals.
service_provided: hypnotherapy sessions (via Zoom), weight loss programs, stop smoking programs, anxiety and stress reduction, sleep improvement, confidence building, procrastination coaching, limiting beliefs removal, self-hypnosis training
